{"layoutParsingResults": [{"prunedResult": {"page_count": null, "width": 2124, "height": 2939, "model_settings": {"use_doc_preprocessor": false, "use_seal_recognition": true, "use_table_recognition": true, "use_formula_recognition": true, "use_chart_recognition": false, "use_region_detection": true, "format_block_content": false, "markdown_ignore_labels": ["number", "footnote", "header", "header_image", "footer", "footer_image", "aside_text"]}, "parsing_res_list": [{"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "渑池杜氏宗谱", "block_bbox": [114, 768, 198, 1526], "block_id": 0, "block_order": 1}, {"block_label": "aside_text", "block_content": "三四三", "block_bbox": [127, 2213, 185, 2345], "block_id": 1, "block_order": null}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "19.必简先祖五言律；子美贤孙三吏诗。\n20.桃仁杏仁柏子仁，仁心待人；天仙凤仙威灵仙，仙方治病。", "block_bbox": [402, 252, 1591, 384], "block_id": 2, "block_order": 2}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "横联：药到病除", "block_bbox": [402, 395, 737, 452], "block_id": 3, "block_order": 3}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "—杜景阳“杜氏中医”联", "block_bbox": [405, 466, 965, 522], "block_id": 4, "block_order": 4}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "21.春酒荐赔阶，北地南天唐丰曲；家门振旅节，经文纬武晋征西。", "block_bbox": [400, 539, 1716, 597], "block_id": 5, "block_order": 5}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "—国民党元老于右仁贺上海浦东高桥镇杜氏宗祠落成", "block_bbox": [407, 611, 1508, 668], "block_id": 6, "block_order": 6}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "22.村在池阳杜诗物候能为证，志存馆内赵客图文足释疑。", "block_bbox": [401, 682, 1535, 740], "block_id": 7, "block_order": 7}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "—安徽贵池市茅坦村志馆联。", "block_bbox": [487, 754, 1025, 811], "block_id": 8, "block_order": 8}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "23.杜撰三别有用心；周全六礼下于人。", "block_bbox": [402, 827, 1170, 883], "block_id": 9, "block_order": 9}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "24.大地春风温我宅；座上嘉宾对酒歌", "block_bbox": [402, 899, 1154, 954], "block_id": 10, "block_order": 10}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "25.友天下士；读古人书", "block_bbox": [402, 970, 874, 1023], "block_id": 11, "block_order": 11}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "—民国杜月笙撰联", "block_bbox": [405, 1040, 824, 1093], "block_id": 12, "block_order": 12}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "26.兆陵世泽；杜甫家声", "block_bbox": [401, 1112, 874, 1165], "block_id": 13, "block_order": 13}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "27.千秋传唱化邪恶启民智人尊文昌；一代怨歌斥叛乱忧黎元世称诗圣。杜曲幸有桑麻田；少陵野老吞声哭。\n", "block_bbox": [402, 1185, 1806, 1313], "block_id": 14, "block_order": 14}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "——杜公祠二联。", "block_bbox": [420, 1324, 769, 1376], "block_id": 15, "block_order": 15}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "28.皇恩三锡厚；祖寿百龄高。", "block_bbox": [420, 1393, 1004, 1448], "block_id": 16, "block_order": 16}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "29.麟阁著鸿篇以来，良将贤臣久已联翩继起，晋则名传武库，唐则像绘凌烟，阀阅播芳馨，所望子孙振奋腾飞，钟鼎旗裳绵旧绪；龙脉自莲山而降，钟灵毓秀尽皆接踵趋前，背有文笔峰环，面有蓉江水绕，阴阳真会合，更堪栋宇辉煌耀日，荣华富贵焕新猷。\n", "block_bbox": [313, 1465, 1912, 1726], "block_id": 17, "block_order": 17}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "30.武库将军府；瀛洲学士家。", "block_bbox": [410, 1744, 993, 1796], "block_id": 18, "block_order": 18}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "31.西蜀诗王府；南阳慈母家。", "block_bbox": [411, 1815, 993, 1865], "block_id": 19, "block_order": 19}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "32.三辅始迁蔚为望族；五化攸叙垂裕后昆。", "block_bbox": [411, 1885, 1257, 1935], "block_id": 20, "block_order": 20}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "33.湖山意气归风雅；台阁文章自典谟。(清·杜煦)", "block_bbox": [412, 1954, 1418, 2007], "block_id": 21, "block_order": 21}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "34.谷嶂前朝九曲，龙环永护九郎祖德；罗山后枕三滩，水绕长怀三赋芳声。", "block_bbox": [411, 2023, 1892, 2079], "block_id": 22, "block_order": 22}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "35.创业耀丰功，前归善后永安，立祠好义泮池，工部香灯千古旺；", "block_bbox": [414, 2095, 1711, 2148], "block_id": 23, "block_order": 23}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "开基炫伟跡，承京兆绪樊川，宦显瀛洲西蜀，武库芳声世代扬。", "block_bbox": [474, 2164, 1715, 2220], "block_id": 24, "block_order": 24}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "36.世系分京兆；家声绍宝田。", "block_bbox": [415, 2238, 998, 2289], "block_id": 25, "block_order": 25}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "宝田家声远；诗史世泽长。", "block_bbox": [477, 2307, 1003, 2359], "block_id": 26, "block_order": 26}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "—紫金蓝塘镇元吉村田碣城百寿楼杜氏祠堂两联", "block_bbox": [500, 2378, 1410, 2433], "block_id": 27, "block_order": 27}], "layout_det_res": {"boxes": [{"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.8209488391876221, "coordinate": [313.57122802734375, 1465.105224609375, 1912.26025390625, 1726.231201171875]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.6095706820487976, "coordinate": [402.646728515625, 325.84735107421875, 1589.92041015625, 381.11798095703125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.5953178405761719, "coordinate": [400.73614501953125, 539.3955078125, 1716.261474609375, 597.73291015625]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.5934352278709412, "coordinate": [401.478271484375, 682.56689453125, 1535.070068359375, 740.320068359375]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.5798285603523254, "coordinate": [412.47113037109375, 1954.929931640625, 1418.58447265625, 2007.537841796875]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.5768683552742004, "coordinate": [411.985107421875, 2023.8001708984375, 1892.54833984375, 2079.29833984375]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.5681775212287903, "coordinate": [420.26275634765625, 1393.902587890625, 1004.2074584960938, 1448.17822265625]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.5675545334815979, "coordinate": [402.327392578125, 1185.36669921875, 1806.703857421875, 1313.16357421875]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.5660279989242554, "coordinate": [404.7779541015625, 253.82057189941406, 1177.5599365234375, 309.5107421875]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.5635419487953186, "coordinate": [402.0879211425781, 827.204345703125, 1170.42724609375, 883.700439453125]}, {"cls_id